     * | (or 3)                          |    A v  = |    A p |    A p                |    A p                                             |    A p                                             |    A p                |
     * | {@see GL46::GL_RGBA}            |    C v  = |    C s |     C p  &amp;it; C s |     C p  &amp;it;   1 - A s    + C s  &amp;it; A s |     C p  &amp;it;   1 - C s    + C c  &amp;it; C s |     C p  + C s        |
