     *
     * | {@see GL46::GL_TEXTURE}       | {@see GL46::GL_SRC_COLOR}           |    C s      |
     * |                               | {@see GL46::GL_ONE_MINUS_SRC_COLOR} |    1 -  C s |
     * |                               | {@see GL46::GL_SRC_ALPHA}           |    A s      |
     * |                               | {@see GL46::GL_ONE_MINUS_SRC_ALPHA} |    1 -  A s |
     * | {@see GL46::GL_TEXTUREn}      | {@see GL46::GL_SRC_COLOR}           |    C s      |
     * |                               | {@see GL46::GL_ONE_MINUS_SRC_COLOR} |    1 -  C s |
