     * |                               | {@see GL46::GL_ONE_MINUS_SRC_COLOR} |    1 -  C c |
     * |                               | {@see GL46::GL_SRC_ALPHA}           |    A c      |
     * |                               | {@see GL46::GL_ONE_MINUS_SRC_ALPHA} |    1 -  A c |
